						<p>Slab standing in the Mahalingēśvara temple at the hamlet Koṇḍāḍi.</p>						

						<p>Ballamahādēvī.</p>						

						<p>This badly worn out and damaged record seems to register a gift of land. All the details are, however, lost.</p>						

